nodes.text: The Veshok Terrace Apartments was a section of living quarter apartments located in the the Justicar territory on the planet Coruscant, named for the veshok trees of Mandalore.
The Veshok Terrace Apartments first appeared in Star Wars Legends in the massively multiplayer online roleplaying game Star Wars: The Old Republic, created by BioWare and released December 20, 2011.
